CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 12, 1961, pg. 20, reads: "Six Tan Aces in Jaycee All-Star Game - Snagger - Although Robert Scott, of Connellsville High, is a great ball packer, he also will figure in a pass pattern, Saturday night, against the Allegheny County eleven - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Western Pennsylvania All-Star Jaycee football player no. 8 Robert Scott leaping with ball
